{"id":953977427,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 month, 1 week","timestamp":1684597847,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"77 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/953977427/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Make Array Empty","memory":"62 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public long countOperationsToEmptyArray(int[] nums) {\n        HashMap<Integer,Integer> hm=new HashMap<>();\n        for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){\n            hm.put(nums[i],i);\n        }\n        Arrays.sort(nums);\n        long ans=0;\n        int n=nums.length;\n        for(int i=1;i<nums.length;i++){\n            if(hm.get(nums[i]) <hm.get(nums[i-1])){\n                ans+=n-i;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans+n;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"make-array-empty","has_notes":false}
